title: Tin Foil Hat Ep 16: The Political Vigilante Graham Elwood
description:
Thank you for tuning into another episode of Tin Foil Hat with Sam Tripoli! This week, Sam and Ryan welcome comedian and political youtube superstar Graham Elwood to the show. On this episode we discuss...
1)The CIA
2)Operation Mockingbird
3)False Flags
4)Neo Liberal and Neo Cons
5)The Committee of 300
